{"tid":1931570,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"獲批取831港鐵站片段　教大生擬向警索償六位數金額","createTime":"2020-03-18T08:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T10:10:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4e7578000126f66e93976e36392aa7d8332ef321","tid":1931570,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】高等法院下令，港鐵須向一名教大學生交出8月31日當晚，在太子站及荔枝角站閉路電視片段，以供他作證據向警方索償。<br />\n<br />\n教大學生梁耀霆稱，去年8月31日晚上路過太子站時，被警方無理襲擊及拘捕，決定向警方索償，並入稟申請「第三方披露令」，要求港鐵交出閉路電視片段作為索償證據。<br />\n<br />\n高等法院下令港鐵須於七日內，向梁耀霆交出太子站及荔枝角站，在8月31日晚至9月1日凌晨的閉路電視片段，而梁耀霆只可將片段用於索償，不得自行複製或用於其他目的。<br />\n<br />\n梁耀霆指會跟律師團隊，仔細研究片段內容，初步計劃索償金額六位數字。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=384788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D384788&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF82proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=776747ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D384788&h=34ea3a7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=384788</a>"},{"pid":"7e5cb3a88de9e4b46f6ffb9ec73a2e75bbfe6529","tid":1931570,"uid":293698,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:37:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df04437ab7900fb9171dcdcbe9480699a5a6f6a1","tid":1931570,"uid":293673,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:38:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19636ff997cd227fdb6be56303535e90911a6fe3","tid":1931570,"uid":122134,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"2百幾億<br />\n拎佢6位數<br />\n都幾大方<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694984d713e3b2b7f8735a7fbef0fd3071faf737","tid":1931570,"uid":42182,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:46:31.000Z","msg":"如果在場受害者人人都6位數字就有排計"},{"pid":"737243800ef60f6951f4c7f48a925316d21ddb